description: Another FrankenMechs collection (exclusive to Pirates/Periphery) and some unorthodox field refit variants. There is a Locust with a big gun, some decapitated Spider+Flea with a big gun, a big gun wanna-be Hollander-Javelin, and good variants of Javelin, Cicada and Catapult. Also, a big arm/big punch Hunchback, the Black Marauder, and the Urbinator.
author: Volfegan
